                "id": "rule_13",
                "type": "rule",
                "content": {
                  "text": "- `cmd/` - Application entry points\n- `internal/` - Private application code (intake, kubernetes controller)\n- `pkg/` - Public packages (aws, performance, resource store)\n- `config/` - K8s manifests and Kustomize\n- `ebpf/` - eBPF programs and build system",
