              {
                "id": "rule_14",
                "type": "rule",
                "content": {
                  "text": "- **In-memory storage** for development/testing\n- **Event-driven subscriptions** for real-time updates\n- **RDF triplet relationships** (subject, predicate, object)\n- **Efficient indexing** for complex queries",
                  "originalHeader": "BadgerDB Integration"
