              {
                "id": "rule_15",
                "type": "rule",
                "content": {
                  "text": "- **Streaming gRPC** for efficient data upload\n- **Batched deltas** with configurable batch sizes\n- **Exponential backoff** for connection failures\n- **Stream recovery** with automatic reconnection\n- **Heartbeat mechanism** for connection health",
                  "originalHeader": "Intake Service Communication"
                },
                "metadata": {
                  "strength": "SHOULD",
                  "format": "ListItem",
                  "line_start": 168,
                  "line_end": 172
